title: Kenny Vs Spenny 408 - First Guy To Stop Singing Loses
description: Just in time for your Christmas caroling, the first one to stop singing loses in this surprisingly grueling competition. Kenny explores various musical genres while creating a fictitious and hideously slanderous version of Spenny&#039;s family tree. Spenny decides to get motivated by singing for charity, trying to raise money to buy a piano for a community center.
